 search for\ndynamical connections between the olivine-dominated asteroids and asteroid\nfamilies found no genetic link (of the type core-mantel-crust) between these\nobjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2013 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2013 21:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
